# ============================================================
# Frontend build-time environment / 前端构建期变量
# ============================================================
# These variables are loaded by Vite from `frontend/.env*` at build/dev time
# (`pnpm dev` / `pnpm build`). They are NOT read from the repo-root `.env`.
# 这些变量由 Vite 在构建/开发时从 `frontend/.env*` 加载（`pnpm dev` /
# `pnpm build`），不会从仓库根目录的 `.env` 读取。
#
# Copy this file to `frontend/.env` (gitignored) and adjust as needed.
# 把本文件复制为 `frontend/.env`（已被 gitignore），按需调整。

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Brand / 品牌
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Override the displayed product name, tagline and meta description.
# Empty = upstream defaults. Affects browser tab title, <meta description>,
# login page logo text, project lobby header, and every user-visible string
# that uses the i18n `[[brand]]` placeholder — see frontend/src/branding.ts.
# 覆盖 UI 中显示的产品名、副标题与 <meta description>。留空则使用上游默认值。
# 影响浏览器标签标题、meta 描述、登录页 Logo 文案、项目大厅顶部等所有用户可见
# 位置（包括 i18n 里 `[[brand]]` 占位符）— 详见 frontend/src/branding.ts。
VITE_BRAND_NAME=第九镜头
VITE_BRAND_TAGLINE=AI 智能视频创作平台
VITE_BRAND_DESCRIPTION=第九镜头 - AI 智能视频创作平台，一键生成广告、短剧、营销视频，让创意无限可能。

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Static brand assets (cannot be overridden via env)
# 品牌静态资产（无法通过环境变量覆盖）
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Logos, favicons and the PWA manifest live as plain files under
# `frontend/public/`. They are fetched directly by the browser, so an env var
# can't switch them. To rebrand them, **replace the files in place**:
#
#   frontend/public/favicon.ico
#   frontend/public/favicon-16x16.png
#   frontend/public/favicon-32x32.png
#   frontend/public/apple-touch-icon.png
#   frontend/public/android-chrome-192x192.png
#   frontend/public/android-chrome-512x512.png
#   frontend/public/android-chrome-maskable-192x192.png
#   frontend/public/android-chrome-maskable-512x512.png
#   frontend/public/site.webmanifest      # also update "name" / "short_name"
#
# After replacing, run `pnpm build` (or restart `pnpm dev`) to pick them up.
#
# Logo / favicon / PWA manifest 是 `frontend/public/` 下的纯静态文件，浏览器
# 直接抓取，无法通过环境变量切换。要改 logo 请**就地替换上述 9 个文件**，并
# 同步修改 `site.webmanifest` 里的 `name` / `short_name` 字段，然后重新执行
# `pnpm build`（或重启 `pnpm dev`）即可生效。
